metadata.name: Bullseye (Nude #75)
metadata.description:
I shot this series of photos using my projector and a video with random visuals. As the shoot went on, the visual turned into a patter of these circles as my model was lying down on the circled matt.

During post-production I got the idea to name it Bullseye. I later spent several months making this NFT on After Effects & Premiere Pro.
